      and boarding station.
    Complete: 0
  - Title: Starter content
    Description: Run starter generators for abilities, combat/status, enemy AI, bosses,
      quests, items, and spells.
    Complete: 0
  - Title: Unity compile
    Description: Open Unity and resolve any project-specific compiler errors.
    Complete: 0
